description: OPPO Reno8 Pro 5G is a 4K night video pioneer with the help with it’s flagship level ultra clear imaging processor “Marisilicon X NPU”, furthermore, The OPPO-exclusive Sony IMX709 32MP front camera, co-made with Sony, using 4-in-1 technology to insert W (transparent) pixels in each RGGB pixel. It is among the first rows and as the top rating to be get certified of TÜV SÜD 36-Month Fluency Rating A Certification. OPPO Reno8 Pro offers 8GB RAM + 256GB ROM with RAM Expansion. When the mobile phone has insufficient memory, this function can be enabled so that part of the free memory can be temporarily used as RAM.
